Varlink is plain-text, type-safe, discoverable, self-documenting and remotable.

%package     -n varlink-bash-completion
Summary:        Bash Completion for %{name}
Group:          System/Shells
Requires:       bash-completion
Requires:       varlink-util = %{version}
